[
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">When <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">spoke</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> there was <st data-num=\"07578\" class=\"\">terror</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> was <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">exalted</st><n id=\"4\" /> in <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but he <st data-num=\"0816\" class=\"\">became guilty</st> by worshiping <st data-num=\"01168\" class=\"\">Baal</st> and <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">died</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Even <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> they <st data-num=\"03254\" class=\"\">persist</st> in <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sin</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">make</st> <st data-num=\"04541\" class=\"\">metal images</st> for themselves,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06091\" class=\"\">idols</st> that they <st data-num=\"08394\" class=\"\">skillfully</st> fashion<n id=\"2\" /> from their own <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of them are nothing but the <st data-num=\"04639\" class=\"\">work</st> of <st data-num=\"02796\" class=\"\">craftsmen</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">There is a</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st> about them:<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">Those</st> who <st data-num=\"02076\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st><n id=\"4\" /> to the calf idol are <st data-num=\"05695\" class=\"\">calf</st> <st data-num=\"05401\" class=\"\">kissers</st>!\u201d<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">Therefore</st> they will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">disappear</st> like<n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"01242\" class=\"\">morning</st> <st data-num=\"06051\" class=\"\">mist</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">like <st data-num=\"07925\" class=\"\">early morning</st> <st data-num=\"02919\" class=\"\">dew</st> that <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">evaporates</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">like <st data-num=\"04671\" class=\"\">chaff</st> that is <st data-num=\"05590\" class=\"\">blown away</st><n id=\"4\" /> from a <st data-num=\"01637\" class=\"\">threshing floor</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">like <st data-num=\"06227\" class=\"\">smoke</st> that disappears through an <st data-num=\"0699\" class=\"\">open window</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> am the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">who brought you out of <st data-num=\"0776 04714\">Egypt</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Therefore, you must <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">acknowledge</st> any <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"02108\" class=\"\">but</st> me.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01115\" class=\"\">Except</st> for me <st data-num=\"0369\">there is no</st> <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">Savior</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">cared for</st><n id=\"1\" /> you in the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">in the <st data-num=\"0776 08514\">dry desert where no water was</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">When they were <st data-num=\"04830\" class=\"\">fed</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> they <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">became satisfied</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">when they <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">were satisfied</st>, <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">they</st> <st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">became proud</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">as a result</st>, they <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">forgot</st> me!</p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">So<n id=\"1\" /> I will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">pounce</st> on them <st data-num=\"03644\" class=\"\">like</st> a <st data-num=\"07826\" class=\"\">lion</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">like a <st data-num=\"05246\" class=\"\">leopard</st> I will <st data-num=\"07789\" class=\"\">lurk</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">by</st> the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">path</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"06298\" class=\"\">attack</st> them like a <st data-num=\"01677\" class=\"\">bear</st> <st data-num=\"07909\" class=\"\">robbed of her cubs</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07167\" class=\"\">rip open</st> their <st data-num=\"05458 03820\">chests</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">devour</st> them <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st> like a <st data-num=\"03833\" class=\"\">lion</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">like a <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">wild</st> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">animal</st> would <st data-num=\"01234\" class=\"\">tear</st> them <st data-num=\"01234\" class=\"\">apart</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroy</st> you,<n id=\"1\" /> O <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st><n id=\"2\" /> is there to <st data-num=\"05828\" class=\"\">help</st> you?</p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0165\" class=\"\">Where</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0645\" class=\"\">then</st> is your <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">that he may <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">save</st> you in <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> your <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Where are<n id=\"2\" /> your <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">rulers</st> for <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whom</st> you asked, <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">Give</st> me a <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">princes</st>\u201d? </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">granted</st><n id=\"1\" /> you a <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> in my <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and I will <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">take</st> him <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">away</st> in my <st data-num=\"05678\" class=\"\">wrath</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">punishment</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st> has been <st data-num=\"06887\" class=\"\">decreed</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">his <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">punishment</st> is being <st data-num=\"06845\" class=\"\">stored up</st> for the future.</p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02256\" class=\"\">labor pains</st> of a <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">woman</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">overtake</st> him,<p class=\"poetry\">but the <st data-num=\"01931 01121\">baby</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">lack</st> <st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">wisdom</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">when</st> the <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> arrives,<p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">come out</st> of the <st data-num=\"04866 01121\">womb</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Will I <st data-num=\"06299\" class=\"\">deliver</st> them from the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">power</st> of <st data-num=\"07585\" class=\"\">Sheol</st>? No, I will not!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Will I <st data-num=\"01350\" class=\"\">redeem</st> them from <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">death</st>? No, I will not!<p class=\"poetry\">O <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">Death</st>, <st data-num=\"0165\" class=\"\">bring on</st> your <st data-num=\"01698\" class=\"\">plagues</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">O <st data-num=\"07585\" class=\"\">Sheol</st>, <st data-num=\"0165\" class=\"\">bring on</st> your <st data-num=\"06987\" class=\"\">destruction</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">My <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st> <st data-num=\"05641\" class=\"\">will not show</st> any <st data-num=\"05164\" class=\"\">compassion</st>!<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Even though</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"06500\" class=\"\">flourishes</st> like a <st data-num=\"0260\" class=\"\">reed plant</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">a scorching <st data-num=\"06921\" class=\"\">east wind</st> will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">wind</st> from the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">rising up</st> from the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">desert</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">As a result, his <st data-num=\"04726\" class=\"\">spring</st> will <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">dry up</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">his <st data-num=\"04599\" class=\"\">well</st> will <st data-num=\"02717\" class=\"\">become dry</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">That wind</st><n id=\"3\" /> will <st data-num=\"08154\" class=\"\">spoil</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> his <st data-num=\"02532\" class=\"\">delightful</st> foods<p class=\"poetry\">in the <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">containers</st> in his <st data-num=\"0214\" class=\"\">storehouse</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "13",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">(14:1)<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"08111\" class=\"\">Samaria</st> will <st data-num=\"0816\" class=\"\">be held guilty</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> she <st data-num=\"04784\" class=\"\">rebelled</st> against her <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fall</st> by the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"05768\" class=\"\">infants</st> will be <st data-num=\"07376\" class=\"\">dashed to the ground</st>\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">their<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"02030\" class=\"\">pregnant women</st> will be <st data-num=\"01234\" class=\"\">ripped open</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "16"
  }
]